  "title": "Sales Promoter (6 days / Kallang)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Drive sales performance by meeting and exceeding departmental targets</li>\n  <li>Showcase and demonstrate products effectively at dealer locations to boost brand visibility</li>\n  <li>Partner closely with the Sales Executive to achieve shared sales goals and deliver strong results</li>\n  <li>Develop and nurture positive working relationships with key outlet partners</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service by addressing inquiries and resolving issues efficiently</li>\n  <li>Keep track of market trends and report competitor activities, pricing, and promotions</li>\n  <li>Maintain attractive and organized product displays and concept counters</li>\n  <li>Contribute actively to sales promotions, campaigns, and departmental projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
